org.cripac.isee.vpe.common

Class VideoData

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cripac.isee.vpe.util.tracking.VideoData

  • public class VideoData
extends java.lang.Object
    The VideoData class wraps decoded data of a video. It is assumed that the width, height and channels of each frame in a video are fixed.
    Author:
    Ken Yu, CRIPAC, 2016
